Q: What is the complaint resolution process?
A: 1) Register your complaint via phone, chat, or email. 2) Receive a complaint reference number within 1 hour. 3) A dedicated case manager is assigned within 24 hours. 4) Resolution provided within 5-7 business days for standard cases, 30 days for complex investigations. 5) If unsatisfied, escalate to our Customer Advocacy team at advocacy@nexusfinanci